{"type": "article", "id": 4089, "title": "Normann Copenhagen 滚轮小边桌", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-04T08:30:50Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233353nZoeyLTNHAuKI6sj.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tBlock Table 是丹麦设计品牌 Normann Copenhagen 今年推出的一款滚轮小边桌，出自丹麦设计师 Simon Legald 之手。其爽朗轻盈的色调与造型，搭配可以 360 度旋转的滚轮装置，方便在家中的任何空间使用，是一款多功能且实用性高的家居产品。它既可以用作餐厨推车、居家活动边桌，也可以成为做咖啡桌与床边桌，甚至还可以在工作学习空间做收纳用。提供薄荷绿、珊瑚色、灰色、浅灰色、黑色以及白色 6 种选择，定价 280 美元，<a href=\"http://www.normann-copenhagen.com/products/block-table?v=602205\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233351MhjEPs8UYZ0vJC7F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233351TbygM7hOFSEd4Pxt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233351WLUSrloOkHPBAx3j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233352kdpeaXWRxJLiVthb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233352ATV15XK6dRtZxQy4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<br>\n\n\n"}